column16: Skip Schumaker grounds into a double play, third baseman Jung Ho Kang to first baseman Pedro Alvarez.   Eugenio Suarez out at 3rd.
Tucker Barnhart singles on a bunt ground ball to third baseman Jung Ho Kang.   Eugenio Suarez to 2nd.
Eugenio Suarez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Starling Marte.
Marlon Byrd grounds out, third baseman Jung Ho Kang to first baseman Pedro Alvarez.
Jay Bruce grounds out to first baseman Pedro Alvarez.
Todd Frazier grounds out softly, third baseman Jung Ho Kang to first baseman Pedro Alvarez.
Joey Votto flies out to left fielder Starling Marte.
